'''马可楼'''，又名'''晚餐厅'''（[[拉丁语|拉丁语]]：cenaculum；英语：Cenacle ，Upper Room）是[[新约|新约]]中许多事件的发生地点<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.christusrex.org/www1/ofm/pope/10GPen/12/12GPsh05.html|publisher=Franciscan Custody of the Holy Land|title=The Cenacle|accessdate=20 June 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080915021728/http://www.christusrex.org/www1/ofm/pope/10GPen/12/12GPsh05.html|archive-date=2008-09-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.goisrael.com/Tourism_Eng/Tourist+Information/Christian+Themes/Details/The+Coenaculum+++chr.htm|work=www.goisrael.com|publisher=Israel Ministry of Tourism|title=The Coenaculum|accessdate=20 June 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090621050618/http://www.goisrael.com/Tourism_Eng/Tourist+Information/Christian+Themes/Details/The+Coenaculum+++chr.htm|archive-date=2009-06-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>：

* [[最后的晚餐|最后的晚餐]]；
* [[洗脚礼|耶稣为门徒洗脚]]<ref> {{bibleverse-nb||John|13:4-11}}</ref>
* 耶稣复活后显现<ref>{{bibleverse-nb||Mark|16:14}}</ref><ref>{{bibleverse-nb||Luke|24:33}}</ref><ref> {{bibleverse||John|20:19}}</ref>
* [[耶稣升天|耶稣升天]]后，门徒在此聚集祷告<ref>{{bibleverse||Acts|1:13}}</ref>
* 选出[[使徒马提亚|马提亚]]为使徒<ref>{{bibleverse||Acts|1:15}}</ref>
* 在[[五旬节|五旬节]]，[[圣灵|圣灵]]浇灌在门徒身上<ref>{{bibleverse||Acts|2:1-4}}</ref> 

根据[[天主教百科全书|天主教百科全书]]<ref>[http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/08355a.htm Catholic Encyclopedia: Jerusalem (A.D. 71-1099)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/08355a.htm |date=20080706190312 }}: "During the first Christian centuries the church at this place was the centre of Christianity in Jerusalem, "Holy and glorious Sion, mother of all churches" (Intercession in "[[Liturgy_of_St._James|St. James' Liturgy]]", ed. Brightman, p. 54). Certainly no spot in Christendom can be more venerable than the place of the Last Supper, which became the first Christian church."</ref>: "第一座基督教堂。

